      <h2 id="tldr">TL;DR</h2>
      <p><strong>Runway Gen-3</strong> is the professional choice. It delivers higher resolution video, more consistent characters, and a full editing suite (masking, inpainting, motion tracking, green screen, color grading) plus a developer API. It costs more and takes longer to learn.</p>
      <p><strong>Pika 2.0</strong> is the creative choice. It generates stylized clips faster, costs less at $10/month, and is far easier for beginners to pick up. It lacks the editing depth and API maturity of Runway.</p>
