    <p>Because both platforms bill on credits rather than flat rate, estimate your monthly clip volume before committing. A solo creator producing a handful of short clips per week will likely stay within Pika's Standard tier comfortably. An agency producing daily client deliverables will burn through credits faster and should model Runway's Pro tier against expected output.</p>

